and royal armies are fighting,
on their way to Alubarna Palace.

43
00:02:31,918 --> 00:02:34,721
However, Karoo is hit
by a stray bullet,

44
00:02:34,754 --> 00:02:36,222
and he can go no further.

45
00:02:39,993 --> 00:02:42,362
Mr. 2 closes in.

46
00:02:42,395 --> 00:02:45,198
