begun at the southeast gate,

49
00:02:52,739 --> 00:02:55,441
with Chopper and Usopp
fighting on one side

50
00:02:55,508 --> 00:02:57,677
and Mr. 4 and
Miss Merry Christmas

51
00:02:57,710 --> 00:02:58,745
on the other.

52
00:03:06,619 --> 00:03:08,521
