"Sworn on a Friend's Dream!

53
00:03:08,555 --> 00:03:10,757
The Battle of Molehill,
Block 4."

54
00:03:24,037 --> 00:03:26,639
[USOPP yelling]

55
00:03:34,814 --> 00:03:35,815
Four.

56
00:03:44,324 --> 00:03:46,292
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS]
They're over there!

57
00:03:46,326 --> 00:03:48,294
