68
00:04:13,853 --> 00:04:15,855
Move! Here we go! Off we go!

69
00:04:15,855 --> 00:04:18,291
Would you go? Come on, you slug!

70
00:04:19,325 --> 00:04:20,293
She's underground again!

71
00:04:20,326 --> 00:04:22,528
Usopp, we have no
choice but to keep moving.

72
00:04:22,528 --> 00:04:24,864
If we stop for a second,
we're dead.

73
00:04:24,864 --> 00:04:25,865
I get it.

74
00:04:25,865 --> 00:04:27,533
If we stand still, then
we're just sitting ducks

75
00:04:27,533 --> 00:04:29,002
for them to keep firing at.

76
00:04:31,871 --> 00:04:33,373
[LASSOO sneezes]

77
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:34,507
Here they come!

78
00:04:36,809 --> 00:04:37,844
[MR. 4]
Four!

79
00:04:43,383 --> 00:04:44,384
[CHOPPER yells]

80
00:04:46,052 --> 00:04:48,388
If I can get to that guy
and knock him down...

81
00:04:49,956 --> 00:04:51,724
Just hold on!

82
00:04:51,791 --> 00:04:52,992
The game isn't
going to be any fun

83
00:04:53,026 --> 00:04:54,861
if we don't have a batter,
now is it?

84
00:04:59,065 --> 00:05:00,066
[CHOPPER yells]

85
00:05:00,133 --> 00:05:01,067
Chopper!

86
00:05:01,067 --> 00:05:02,335
[CHOPPER yells]

87
00:05:06,072 --> 00:05:08,341
Whew! Well, at least
I can still do that.

88
00:05:09,542 --> 00:05:10,843
Dirty mole!

89
00:05:12,545 --> 00:05:13,579
[CHOPPER]
Bastard!

90
00:05:17,517 --> 00:05:19,986
Damn, if they keep running away
through these mole tunnels,

91
00:05:20,019 --> 00:05:22,355
even if I use a rumble ball,
I won't have enough time

92
00:05:22,388 --> 00:05:23,856
to do any real damage.

93
00:05:26,893 --> 00:05:29,095
Hey, where is he?

94
00:05:29,095 --> 00:05:30,096
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS]
Huh?

95
00:05:30,163 --> 00:05:31,531
We're missing one of 'em!
Where'd the ugly guy

96
00:05:31,564 --> 00:05:32,865
with the long nose
run off to?

97
00:05:32,899 --> 00:05:34,000
Where is he? Where?

98
00:05:34,867 --> 00:05:37,770
Yeah. I don't see Usopp
around anywhere.

99
00:05:37,770 --> 00:05:40,106
[USOPP] What's the matter?
You guys lose something?

100
00:05:42,842 --> 00:05:44,410
[USOPP]
I gotta say, mole woman,

101
00:05:44,444 --> 00:05:45,778
I'm impressed that you
could dig all these

102
00:05:45,778 --> 00:05:47,947
underground tunnels
in such a short time.

103
00:05:48,014 --> 00:05:49,549
Good work, really!

104
00:05:49,582 --> 00:05:51,684
Then again, there can
be some pretty literal

105
00:05:51,718 --> 00:05:53,853
pitfalls when you
fight like this, I bet.

106
00:05:53,886 --> 00:05:56,022
You should be careful.

107
00:05:56,055 --> 00:05:57,056
Where are you?

108
00:05:57,090 --> 00:05:58,424
Where did you go?

109
00:05:59,625 --> 00:06:00,893
Wait, is he...?

110
00:06:00,927 --> 00:06:03,696
[USOPP] Yep! So kind of you to
dig all these tunnels, really.

111
00:06:03,730 --> 00:06:05,465
You do realize, though,

112
00:06:05,531 --> 00:06:06,966
that you're not the
only one who can crawl

113
