around inside them.

114
00:06:10,737 --> 00:06:12,105
[USOPP]
Usopp...!

115
00:06:12,138 --> 00:06:13,806
You sneaky little rat!

116
00:06:13,806 --> 00:06:16,442
You were hiding
in one of the holes.

117
00:06:16,476 --> 00:06:19,112
[USOPP]
...Pound!

118
00:06:26,486 --> 00:06:27,820
[MR. 4 groans]

119
00:06:30,490 --> 00:06:32,091
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS]
Mr. 4!

120
00:06:32,125 --> 00:06:34,394
[USOPP growls]

121
00:06:36,829 --> 00:06:37,730
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS]
What?!

122
00:06:37,764 --> 00:06:39,999
It looks like he's using
a five‐ton hammer!

123
00:06:40,066 --> 00:06:43,002
How does a string bean like him
have the strength to do that?

124
00:06:50,810 --> 00:06:52,678
That's a big hammer.

125
00:06:52,745 --> 00:06:55,014
Who exactly is this
long‐nosed freak?

126
00:06:57,517 --> 00:06:59,685
[USOPP] I am a traveler
of the world's oceans.

127
00:06:59,685 --> 00:07:02,622
A crusher of notorious monsters,
beasts, and foes.

128
00:07:02,655 --> 00:07:04,190
A sinker of countless ships.

129
00:07:04,257 --> 00:07:06,092
A flattener of numberless towns.

130
00:07:06,125 --> 00:07:07,860
Trembling with fear,
people everywhere

131
00:07:07,860 --> 00:07:10,930
call me the master
of destruction! Heh heh.

132
00:07:10,963 --> 00:07:12,865
I suggest that you take
the time to remember

133
00:07:12,932 --> 00:07:14,133
my name carefully.

134
00:07:15,501 --> 00:07:18,504
I am... Captain Usopp!

135
00:07:19,205 --> 00:07:22,041
Wow! Wow! Wow! Awesome! Awesome!

136
00:07:22,041 --> 00:07:24,610
Yes, yes, thank you very much.
Ah, it's nothing, really.

137
00:07:24,644 --> 00:07:26,479
I'll be signing
autographs later.

138
00:07:26,512 --> 00:07:28,548
[CHOPPER] I thought you
were useless up until now!

139
00:07:28,614 --> 00:07:29,615
[USOPP]
Hey!

140
00:07:31,617 --> 00:07:32,885
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS]
Mr. 4...

141
00:07:34,654 --> 00:07:35,721
[USOPP]
He isn't moving.

142
00:07:35,788 --> 00:07:37,857
Could I have really
hit him that hard?

143
00:07:37,890 --> 00:07:39,725
No, it doesn't matter.

144
00:07:39,725 --> 00:07:41,627
This is my chance
to beat them both.

145
00:07:41,661 --> 00:07:43,663
I have to take it.

146
00:07:43,696 --> 00:07:45,631
[USOPP]
Your turn, penguin!

147
00:07:45,665 --> 00:07:48,701
Now you'll feel the wrath
of my five‐ton hammer!

148
00:07:48,734 --> 00:07:50,069
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS yells]

149
00:07:50,069 --> 00:07:53,806
[USOPP]
Taste my Usopp Pound!

150
00:07:54,507 --> 00:07:57,577
She escaped.
Where are you, penguin?

151
00:07:57,577 --> 00:07:59,812
I told you! I'm a mole,
not a penguin, moron!

152
00:07:59,846 --> 00:08:00,913
Now I see you!

153
00:08:00,913 --> 00:08:02,915
Pound! Pound! Pound! Pound!

154
00:08:02,915 --> 00:08:05,184
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS]
Here! Here! Here! Here!

155
00:08:05,218 --> 00:08:08,254
‐‐Pound! Pound! Pound! Pound!
‐‐Here! Here! Here! Here!

156
00:08:08,321 --> 00:08:09,489
[USOPP]
Rubber band of doom.

157
00:08:09,522 --> 00:08:11,591
‐‐Pound! Pound! Pound! Pound!
‐‐Here! Here! Here! Here!

158
00:08:15,862 --> 00:08:18,531
[USOPP] Damn, you're
everywhere, mole woman!

159
00:08:18,564 --> 00:08:20,600
Ha! Hey, ya missed me,
so what's the point

160
00:08:20,666 --> 00:08:22,602
of that big hammer
[inhales]

161
00:08:22,602 --> 00:08:24,737
if you can't
manage to hit me?

162
00:08:24,770 --> 00:08:27,707
[USOPP chuckles] Let me tell
you something, penguin.

163
00:08:29,108 --> 00:08:31,043
I'm sure you've heard
by now that a good number

164
00:08:31,077 --> 00:08:32,879
of your fellow
Baroque Works agents

165
00:08:32,912 --> 00:08:34,614
have been eliminated by us.

166
00:08:36,015 --> 00:08:39,719
But the truth is it was all me!

167
00:08:39,752 --> 00:08:40,753
You did all that?

168
00:08:40,786 --> 00:08:43,256
[USOPP]
And in addition to that...

169
00:08:43,289 --> 00:08:45,591
I command eight thousand men!

170
00:08:49,128 --> 00:08:51,030
That's awesome!

171
00:08:53,799 --> 00:08:55,301
‐‐Five tons!
‐‐Awesome!

172
00:08:55,368 --> 00:08:57,603
‐‐Five tons!
‐‐Awesome!

173
00:08:57,637 --> 00:08:59,138
‐‐Five tons!
