174
00:08:59,138 --> 00:09:01,607
‐‐Five tons!
‐‐Awesome!

175
00:09:01,641 --> 00:09:03,809
‐‐Five tons!
‐‐Awesome!

176
00:09:03,876 --> 00:09:05,645
[MR. 4]
Ow...

177
00:09:05,711 --> 00:09:07,613
Ah! He has to wake up now?

178
00:09:07,647 --> 00:09:10,116
[CHOPPER] He survived being
hit by a five‐ton hammer?

179
00:09:10,149 --> 00:09:12,084
What kind of monster is he?

180
00:09:12,118 --> 00:09:13,653
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS] Yeah.
He doesn't even have a bump

181
00:09:13,719 --> 00:09:15,321
on his head.

182
00:09:15,388 --> 00:09:18,124
He took a direct blow to the
head from a five‐ton hammer

183
00:09:18,157 --> 00:09:20,760
and he's okay? Why is that?

184
00:09:22,995 --> 00:09:24,163
[LASSOO sneezes]

185
00:09:28,668 --> 00:09:29,335
Four?

186
00:09:29,402 --> 00:09:30,937
[CHOPPER yells]

187
00:09:30,970 --> 00:09:32,672
[CHOPPER]
You mean that thing was a fake?

188
00:09:32,672 --> 00:09:34,273
This whole time?

189
00:09:34,307 --> 00:09:35,775
Of course it was!

190
00:09:35,808 --> 00:09:37,777
You think I can
really lift five tons?

191
00:09:37,810 --> 00:09:40,112
I stop trying after
just 10 pounds!

192
00:09:40,146 --> 00:09:41,847
This is a model I made.

193
00:09:41,914 --> 00:09:44,016
It's only a couple of
frying pans tied to a stick

194
00:09:44,083 --> 00:09:45,318
and covered with paper.

195
00:09:48,187 --> 00:09:50,089
[USOPP gasps]

196
00:09:52,024 --> 00:09:53,659
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS]
Why, you...

197
00:09:53,693 --> 00:09:56,028
You tricked me with
a piece of paper?

198
00:09:56,095 --> 00:09:57,363
No more mercy for you!

199
00:09:59,765 --> 00:10:01,267
Mole Swimming!

200
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:02,835
Mole fish escape!

201
00:10:03,769 --> 00:10:07,006
She's gone underground
into the mole tunnels again.

202
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:08,941
Watch out for
the holes, Chopper!

203
00:10:10,376 --> 00:10:12,111
[USOPP]
What's she planning this time?

204
00:10:24,290 --> 00:10:25,992
[USOPP]
Where are you, mole‐thing?

205
00:10:26,025 --> 00:10:28,060
Where did you go?

206
00:10:28,060 --> 00:10:29,195
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS laughs]

207
00:10:29,228 --> 00:10:31,697
Watch out for the holes,
did you say?

208
00:10:31,731 --> 00:10:34,367
[laughs]
That won't do you any good!

209
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:36,068
Moving around underground
is just like

210
00:10:36,068 --> 00:10:37,870
swimming in a pool to me.

211
00:10:37,903 --> 00:10:39,705
You can't escape this time!

212
00:10:39,739 --> 00:10:44,043
[laughing]

213
00:10:44,076 --> 00:10:45,077
Pool?

214
