Banana!

218
00:10:56,489 --> 00:10:57,890
[USOPP yells]

219
00:10:59,058 --> 00:11:01,193
Mr. 4. Lassoo.

220
00:11:01,227 --> 00:11:03,095
Go ahead and take care
of that reindeer man

221
00:11:03,095 --> 00:11:05,431
‐‐over there, would ya?
‐‐[MR. 4] Four!

222
00:11:05,498 --> 00:11:08,034
Let's show them your
Four Hundred Base Knocks!

223
00:11:15,107 --> 00:11:16,108
[CHOPPER]
It's no use.

224
00:11:16,175 --> 00:11:19,378
There's no way I can
handle an attack like this.

225
00:11:19,412 --> 00:11:21,013
It's all or nothing now.

226
00:11:21,047 --> 00:11:23,249
I have to think up
a way to beat this guy,

227
00:11:23,282 --> 00:11:25,851
and quickly,
before he kills us both!

228
00:11:28,187 --> 00:11:29,188
[CHOPPER]
Rumble!

229
00:11:35,227 --> 00:11:36,362
[CHOPPER]
Brain Point!

230
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:46,205
Scope!

231
00:12:09,061 --> 00:12:11,330
[VIVI panting]

232
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:19,405
[SOLDIERS yelling]

233
00:12:27,613 --> 00:12:30,649
[VIVI]
Koza. Where are you?

234
00:12:30,683 --> 00:12:32,651
What have you done
to our country?

235
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:36,422
[KOZA yelling]

236
00:12:38,691 --> 00:12:39,692
[VIVI grunts]

237
00:12:53,439 --> 00:12:55,775
[VIVI grunts]

238
00:12:57,543 --> 00:13:01,180
[COBRA] Remember,
a country is its people.

239
00:13:01,213 --> 00:13:02,715
[VIVI]
Oh, father!

240
00:13:05,117 --> 00:13:09,488
Don't you have a rebellion
to stop, Princess?

241
00:13:09,522 --> 00:13:11,624
[LUFFY] You want it to work
out so that nobody dies

242
00:13:11,657 --> 00:13:14,527
in this fight,
isn't that right, Vivi?

243
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:16,862
You can't win like that.

244
00:13:17,730 --> 00:13:19,465
[LUFFY]
People die.

245
00:13:19,498 --> 00:13:21,967
[VIVI] Stop talking like that!
I won't listen to it!

246
00:13:22,735 --> 00:13:24,737
[ZORO] If you truly are
the one and only hope

247
00:13:24,804 --> 00:13:26,906
for preventing that tragedy,

248
00:13:26,906 --> 00:13:29,842
then you must survive,
no matter what.

249
00:13:29,875 --> 00:13:32,645
What happens to us isn't
the least bit important!

250
00:13:36,916 --> 00:13:39,585
[KAROO squawks]

251
00:13:39,585 --> 00:13:42,655
You guys, go on ahead!

252
00:13:42,688 --> 00:13:45,758
We'll wait for you in Alubarna!

253
00:13:45,758 --> 00:13:47,927
[LUFFY]
Yeah!

254
00:13:57,069 --> 00:13:58,571
[CROCODILE]
It will be.

255
00:14:00,005 --> 00:14:02,107
The demise of
this pathetic kingdom,

256
00:14:02,107 --> 00:14:03,609
Miss Wednesday.

257
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:09,248
[VIVI]
I'm going to stop this,

258
00:14:09,281 --> 00:14:11,183
no matter what I have to do!

259
00:14:25,764 --> 00:14:26,966
Where's Chopper?

260
00:14:47,786 --> 00:14:48,888
Chopper.

261
00:14:50,089 --> 00:14:51,991
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS] You don't
have time to be worried about

262
00:14:51,991 --> 00:14:53,158
someone else!

263
00:14:55,794 --> 00:14:58,764
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS] I told
you I was done being merciful.

264
00:14:58,797 --> 00:14:59,765
Now, then.

265
00:14:59,798 --> 00:15:01,934
I think I'll torment you
for just a little while

266
00:15:01,967 --> 00:15:04,837
longer before I finish
you off for good.

267
00:15:04,904 --> 00:15:08,307
Here comes my mole banana!

268
00:15:08,340 --> 00:15:10,276
[USOPP yells]

269
00:15:10,309 --> 00:15:11,844
Hey, now. What are you doing?

270
00:15:11,844 --> 00:15:14,246
It's poor form to go
after that spot on a guy!

271
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:17,116
Stop your whining!
You're alive, aren't you?

272
00:15:17,149 --> 00:15:21,020
Mole Banana!
Banana! Banana! Banana!

273
00:15:21,020 --> 00:15:24,857
Banana! Banana! Banana!
Banana! Banana! Banana!

274
00:15:24,857 --> 00:15:26,258
[USOPP]
Perfect!

275
00:15:26,292 --> 00:15:27,826
There's part of a wall there!

276
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:30,095
If I keep running at this
speed and she follows me,

277
00:15:30,129 --> 00:15:33,198
she'll run into the part of
the wall that's under the sand!

278
00:15:33,265 --> 00:15:36,268
And she'll crash
really hard, too!

279
00:15:36,302 --> 00:15:38,170
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS]
Banana! Banana!

280
00:15:38,203 --> 00:15:41,707
[USOPP] Come on! Come on!
Come on! Come on!

281
00:15:41,707 --> 00:15:43,208
Now it's time to split
your head in two,

282
00:15:43,208 --> 00:15:44,543
stupid penguin!

283
00:15:56,221 --> 00:15:57,222
[USOPP yells]

284
00:16:05,898 --> 00:16:07,633
[USOPP yells]

285
00:16:12,137 --> 00:16:13,238
Usopp.

286
00:16:19,044 --> 00:16:20,980
[CHOPPER yells]

287
00:16:22,414 --> 00:16:23,882
[MR. 4]
Four.

288
00:16:40,366 --> 00:16:41,367
Usopp.

289
00:16:53,746 --> 00:16:55,948
[CHOPPER] No, I can't
be worried about that.

290
00:16:55,948 --> 00:16:58,784
The Rumble Ball will only
last for two more minutes.

291
00:16:58,784 --> 00:17:00,185
Usopp will be fine.

292
00:17:00,219 --> 00:17:02,287
It'll take more than
that to finish him.

293
00:17:02,354 --> 00:17:05,124
Right now, finding the enemy's
weakness comes first.

294
00:17:05,190 --> 00:17:07,726
Otherwise, we are
going to die here.

295
00:17:07,760 --> 00:17:09,962
I just have to remember
what Usopp told me

296
00:17:09,962 --> 00:17:11,697
back on the ship.

297
00:17:11,730 --> 00:17:12,798
Right now...

298
00:17:12,865 --> 00:17:15,868
I just have to do
whatever I can!

299
00:17:43,662 --> 00:17:44,897
[USOPP]
Hi‐ya!

300
00:17:47,966 --> 00:17:49,001
[USOPP]
Hi‐ya!

301
00:17:51,003 --> 00:17:54,940
[USOPP chuckles]

302
00:17:54,973 --> 00:17:56,408
[laughing]

303
00:17:56,442 --> 00:17:57,609
Got crushed, huh?

304
00:17:57,643 --> 00:17:59,912
Well it serves you right, you
stupid old penguin woman!

305
00:17:59,945 --> 00:18:02,147
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS] A mole!
I'm a mole, you moron!

306
00:18:02,181 --> 00:18:03,148
[USOPP screams]

307
00:18:03,182 --> 00:18:04,416
Molehill Highway!

308
00:18:06,318 --> 00:18:08,087
[USOPP yells]

309
00:18:08,120 --> 00:18:10,489
[USOPP] What are you doing?
Let me go!

310
00:18:10,522 --> 00:18:13,025
Stop it, already! This is
too dangerous to do out here!

311
00:18:13,025 --> 00:18:14,693
If you're not careful,
we'll run into something!

312
00:18:14,693 --> 00:18:16,462
Ahh! Like that wall
in front of you!

313
00:18:16,495 --> 00:18:18,664
Look ahead! A wall, a wall!

314
00:18:18,697 --> 00:18:21,667
Help! I'm too young to die!

315
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:24,036
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS]
Mole‐mole Impact!

316
00:18:24,036 --> 00:18:25,037
[USOPP grunts]

317
00:18:30,209 --> 00:18:31,944
[USOPP yelling]

318
00:18:34,379 --> 00:18:37,049
[CHOPPER] I got it!
I see your weakness now!

319
00:18:46,458 --> 00:18:48,527
[CHOPPER yelling]

320
00:18:56,735 --> 00:18:57,970
[CHOPPER]
Now!

321
00:18:59,204 --> 00:19:00,906
[LASSOO]

322
00:19:02,407 --> 00:19:04,076
[CHOPPER]
Usopp!

323
00:19:04,143 --> 00:19:05,410
Usopp, can you get up?

324
00:19:05,410 --> 00:19:08,013
Come on, Usopp!

325
00:19:08,046 --> 00:19:10,215
Stay away from the mole
and all the holes, too!

326
00:19:12,084 --> 00:19:14,219
You don't have to tell me twice!
I'm going!

327
00:19:15,554 --> 00:19:16,755
[CHOPPER]
Hurry up!

328
00:19:16,755 --> 00:19:19,258
What exactly are those
morons doing now?

329
00:19:30,536 --> 00:19:31,703
[USOPP whines]

330
00:19:34,273 --> 00:19:36,408
[USOPP, CHOPPER yell]

331
00:19:42,781 --> 00:19:44,116
What's that?

332
00:19:57,696 --> 00:20:00,566
And that's the
molehill's weakness.

333
00:20:00,599 --> 00:20:02,634
All of the tunnels are
connected to each other

334
00:20:02,634 --> 00:20:04,136
in one big network.

335
00:20:05,304 --> 00:20:06,305
Oh?

336
00:20:08,473 --> 00:20:09,641
Yeah?

337
00:20:31,263 --> 00:20:32,397
[CHOPPER]
They're alive?

338
00:20:32,431 --> 00:20:33,665
This isn't good!

339
00:20:33,665 --> 00:20:35,434
My Rumble Ball's
effectiveness is already

340
00:20:35,467 --> 00:20:36,768
half‐gone by now!

341
00:20:39,171 --> 00:20:41,306
[USOPP whimpers]

342
00:20:41,340 --> 00:20:42,574
No more.

343
00:20:42,608 --> 00:20:43,842
[CHOPPER]
Huh?

344
00:20:43,842 --> 00:20:47,079
No more of this!
I don't wanna die in this place!

345
00:20:47,112 --> 00:20:47,913
Usopp, wait!

346
00:20:47,946 --> 00:20:49,748
No way, I'm outta here!
I've had it!

347
00:20:49,781 --> 00:20:51,516
There's no way
to beat these two!

348
00:20:51,583 --> 00:20:54,253
Not when they're still
alive after that explosion!

349
00:20:54,286 --> 00:20:55,787
Running away from
them isn't going to do

350
00:20:55,821 --> 00:20:57,422
any good, don't you see?

351
00:20:57,456 --> 00:20:59,091
[USOPP panting]

352
00:20:59,124 --> 00:21:00,259
[CHOPPER]
Usopp!

353
00:21:00,292 --> 00:21:02,127
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS] The Blue
nose is right, you know.

354
00:21:02,160 --> 00:21:04,129
[USOPP yells]

355
00:21:04,529 --> 00:21:07,099
[MISS MERRY CHRISTMAS] That was
quite a little stunt you pulled!

356
00:21:07,132 --> 00:21:08,300
After doing something like that,

357
00:21:08,333 --> 00:21:09,701
we're not gonna just
let you run away

358
00:21:09,701 --> 00:21:11,603
like nothing happened.

359
00:21:11,637 --> 00:21:13,205
Oh, no! Usopp!

360
00:21:13,205 --> 00:21:18,277
[USOPP yelling]

361
00:21:18,310 --> 00:21:20,212
Well, I guess with a
captain who's so pathetic,

362
00:21:20,279 --> 00:21:22,714
it's no surprise that the
rest of the crew's useless.

363
00:21:27,719 --> 00:21:29,721
[USOPP]
Captain? Wait.

364
00:21:29,721 --> 00:21:32,524
Are you‐‐
Are you talking about Luffy?

365
00:21:32,557 --> 00:21:34,226
If you're talking
about the Straw Hat kid,

366
00:21:34,293 --> 00:21:36,528
that idiot was killed a little
while ago by the boss.

367
00:21:36,561 --> 00:21:38,163
What a shocker.

368
00:21:38,196 --> 00:21:41,566
And now the rebellion has
started and is well under way.

369
00:21:41,633 --> 00:21:43,568
Well. I guess you
picked the wrong people

370
00:21:43,635 --> 00:21:44,636
to mess with.

371
00:21:51,877 --> 00:21:54,379
She said Luffy is dead?

372
00:21:57,816 --> 00:22:00,185
Don't you dare lie to us!

373
00:22:12,898 --> 00:22:17,269
<i>♪I couldn't say just how long</i>
<i>I've wanted to</i>

374
00:22:17,269 --> 00:22:24,209
<i>Tell you everything</i>
<i>yet I could not begin to</i>

375
00:22:24,242 --> 00:22:28,613
<i>Now, I'm here beside you</i>
<i>and I know</i>

376
00:22:28,613 --> 00:22:34,453
<i>That the glimmer that I see,</i>
is my dream revived

377
00:22:34,453 --> 00:22:39,891
<i>Kindly, your smile</i>
<i>is all I can see</i>

378
00:22:39,925 --> 00:22:43,729
<i>Happiness is what</i>
<i>you've given me</i>

379
00:22:43,762 --> 00:22:47,799
And my heart feels so free

380
00:22:47,799 --> 00:22:50,369
<i>Glory, glory, now I shine</i>

381
00:22:50,402 --> 00:22:53,438
<i>Because you're here with me</i>

382
00:22:53,472 --> 00:22:58,877
<i>Wipe away these tears of mine</i>
for they turn to bravery

383
00:22:58,910 --> 00:23:01,413
<i>What I want is to be strong</i>

384
00:23:01,446 --> 00:23:04,449
<i>And to share this fight with you</i>

385
00:23:04,483 --> 00:23:10,489
<i>And someday,</i>
I know we'll get there... ♪

386
00:23:17,662 --> 00:23:18,663
[CHOPPER]
Luffy's been killed?

387
00:23:18,663 --> 00:23:21,333
[USOPP] Quit lying to us,
you freaky mole‐woman.

388
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:23,902
Luffy... Luffy can't be dead!

389
00:23:23,935 --> 00:23:25,103
[CHOPPER]
Usopp!

390
00:23:25,137 --> 00:23:27,839
[SANJI] Ha! You're really
getting annoying, ballerina boy.

391
00:23:27,906 --> 00:23:29,808
And your Clone‐Clone
powers aren't going to

392
00:23:29,841 --> 00:23:31,410
do you any good, either.

393
00:23:31,443 --> 00:23:32,944
So what if your face
changes a bit?

394
00:23:32,978 --> 00:23:34,646
Come on, let's see
what you've got!

395
00:23:34,679 --> 00:23:36,281
[LUFFY]
On the next One Piece!

396
00:23:36,314 --> 00:23:39,851
"Big Opening Day Today!
The Copy‐Copy Montage!"

397
00:23:39,918 --> 00:23:41,853
I'm gonna be
King of the Pirates!

